name: MINI MYRTLE
description: 'Oh yes she did'!  Companion piece to 'MYRTLE'. Daughter of 'Mama Myrtle', MINI MYRTLE seems to have many of the same unique attributes as her very fearless mom.  MINI MYRTLE will follow the sound advice given to her by her feathered mom - 'BE THE BIRD...YOU WERE BORN TO BE!'  Painting by Richard Lorenz 2021
